1
00:01:08,959 --> 00:01:11,000
Liu Xiang and Shen Qing were best friends.

2
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,920
Shen Qing was beautiful

3
00:01:13,239 --> 00:01:14,239
and outgoing.

4
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:16,239
So Xu Wenwen took an interest in her,

5
00:01:16,439 --> 00:01:17,560
and groomed her carefully.

6
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:18,519
Su Zhuang

7
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:20,599
was reeled in using Shen Qing as bait.

8
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:21,959
Hey,

9
00:01:22,239 --> 00:01:24,400
is your husband still hitting you?

10
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,400
If he hits you,

11
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,560
call the police and have him arrested.

12
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,840
I'll hire a lawyer for your divorce.

13
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:31,760
Thank you, Chairwoman Xu.

14
00:01:33,439 --> 00:01:34,239
I...

15
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:37,159
Could I ask you for a favor?

16
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:40,120
I consider you family.

17
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,760
Just speak your mind.

18
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:44,079
Could you let Shen Qing

19
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:46,280
leave Su Zhuang?

20
00:01:48,319 --> 00:01:49,239
What happened?

21
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,079
What exactly did Qingqing tell you?

22
00:01:53,719 --> 00:01:54,640
A few days ago,

23
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,480
on the anniversary of her mother's death,

24
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,439
she got drunk and told me

25
00:02:00,959 --> 00:02:02,799
she's pregnant with Su Zhuang's child.

26
00:02:03,319 --> 00:02:05,319
If she's carrying Su Zhuang's child,

27
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,959
why would she want to leave him?

28
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,800
She said over the years,

29
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,400
she's helped Su Zhuang do a lot of dirty work.

30
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,199
She's scared.

31
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,759
She also showed me

32
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,439
a video.

33
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:16,960
What video?

34
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:19,240
A video of Su Zhuang taking advantage

35
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,599
of her drunk state to assault her.

36
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:26,560
Did Qingqing ask you to tell me this?

37
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,560
I'm afraid she'll sink deeper and deeper,

38
00:02:30,919 --> 00:02:32,280
and eventually destroy herself.

39
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:34,759
Drunken words don't count.

40
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:37,319
She said Su Zhuang will end up in jail.

41
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,439
He's pocketed a lot of money over the years,

42
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,120
and she's kept track of every cent.

43
00:02:48,159 --> 00:02:50,080
After that conversation,

44
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:51,560
Xu Wenwen knew

45
00:02:51,919 --> 00:02:53,360
her secret was exposed.

46
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:56,599
So she decided to use Feng Bing

47
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,520
to get rid of Liu Xiang.

48
00:03:10,439 --> 00:03:11,560
Tell me,

49
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,840
isn't this fate?

50
00:03:14,599 --> 00:03:15,360
Liu Xiang

51
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,360
wasn't killed by Feng Bing,

52
00:03:18,759 --> 00:03:21,599
but died at the hands of Ma Shijiang.

53
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,599
If it weren't for that loser,

54
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:26,400
none of what followed would have happened.

55
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:28,439
Shen Qing

56
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:30,879
wouldn't have died either.

57
00:03:32,599 --> 00:03:33,199
Why?

58
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,680
Shen Qing was actually Xu Wenwen's

59
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:37,280
mole planted by Su Zhuang's side.

60
00:03:37,879 --> 00:03:38,800
After Liu Xiang died,

61
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:40,759
she naturally suspected Xu Wenwen.

62
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,039
On top of that,

63
00:03:43,639 --> 00:03:44,800
the loan fraud was exposed.

64
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:47,759
Xu Wenwen made up her mind

65
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,039
to eliminate Shen Qing.

66
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,159
This woman

67
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:53,800
is truly ruthless.

68
00:03:54,719 --> 00:03:56,439
Did Xu Wenwen send you to kill Shen Qing?

69
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,560
I was supposed to go,

70
00:04:00,879 --> 00:04:02,080
but Xing Mingliang went instead.

71
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:05,560
That makes sense.

72
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,680
That day, behind the bank,

73
00:04:10,159 --> 00:04:11,800
the person on the motorcycle in the alley

74
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,000
wearing red gloves

75
00:04:13,639 --> 00:04:14,520
was Xing Mingliang.

76
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,680
Does she still like wearing red gloves?

77
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:24,839
Yes.

78
00:04:25,839 --> 00:04:26,920
Very much.

79
00:04:30,959 --> 00:04:32,120
I really never imagined

80
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:35,959
the Red Glove from 22 years ago

81
00:04:37,399 --> 00:04:38,360
was actually a woman.

82
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,519
Back then,

83
00:04:44,199 --> 00:04:45,920
she always dressed like a man.

84
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,759
She even bound her chest

85
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,319
tightly with cloth.

86
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,560
Makes perfect sense, actually.

87
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,600
Mixed in with a bunch of men,

88
00:04:55,319 --> 00:04:57,560
doing such despicable business,

89
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,560
she had to disguise herself

90
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,759
to make herself appear strong.

91
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:08,040
We're still searching Xu Wenwen's club.

92
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,120
No red gloves found yet.

93
00:05:14,759 --> 00:05:15,839
In the reception room,

94
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:18,199
there's a hidden mechanism.

95
00:07:46,399 --> 00:07:48,560
Did you kill Shen Qing?

96
00:07:49,199 --> 00:07:50,839
Xu Wenwen forced me to.

97
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,360
After the Red Glove case broke,

98
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,519
she knew I was the one who incited Ma Shijiang.

99
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:57,560
She made me drive my father's car

100
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,800
to take Ma Shijiang out of Fengdu.

101
00:08:00,399 --> 00:08:02,879
After that, she made me obey her every order.

102
00:08:03,079 --> 00:08:04,680
Otherwise, she'd send me to prison.

103
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:05,879
Of course,

104
00:08:06,879 --> 00:08:08,319
she would satisfy my demands.

105
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,680
Xu Wenwen told me

106
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,800
she'd already hinted to Su Zhuang

107
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:18,600
that Shen Qing would bring them massive trouble.

108
00:08:20,399 --> 00:08:22,720
After Shen Qing escaped from home that night,

109
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:24,800
she had me follow Su Zhuang

110
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,959
up to the rooftop of the bank.

111
00:08:28,199 --> 00:08:28,879
She said,

112
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:30,800
if Su Zhuang hesitated,

113
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:33,919
I was to do it myself.

114
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:42,840
Don't say a word.

115
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,360
Keep going up.

116
00:08:48,639 --> 00:08:49,559
Get up there.

117
00:08:52,759 --> 00:08:53,679
Keep walking!

118
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,440
Wait.

119
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:04,120
Wait, wait, wait.

120
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:09,600
I... I'm pregnant.

121
00:09:09,879 --> 00:09:12,320
Can you please let me go?

122
00:09:13,879 --> 00:09:14,679
Turn around.

123
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:19,240
Step up there.

124
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:20,960
Hurry up.

125
00:09:23,679 --> 00:09:24,679
Move up.

126
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,600
It was only

127
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:51,120
after Ma Shijiang's crimes

128
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,759
that you met Xu Wenwen.

129
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:55,000
So how could you know the details

130
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:57,559
of the 531 case from 22 years ago?

131
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,159
As far back as I can remember,

132
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,080
my father would stay out all night,

133
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:04,759
poring over case files at the office.

134
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:06,919
As I grew older,

135
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:08,919
my curiosity

136
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:10,720
grew stronger and stronger.

137
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:13,279
So I sneaked a peek when he wasn't looking.

138
00:10:13,879 --> 00:10:15,200
That was when

139
00:10:15,759 --> 00:10:17,639
I first learned about the Red Gloves.

140
00:10:19,759 --> 00:10:20,679
Later on,

141
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:22,799
I wanted to experience

142
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:25,320
what it felt like to wear those red gloves.

143
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:28,519
So I secretly bought a pair myself.

144
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:32,759
And Meng Yu?

145
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:34,720
The truth is,

146
00:10:35,879 --> 00:10:37,799
he was secretly protecting Ruolan.

147
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:46,360
You're just making excuses for your crimes.

148
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,919
I advise you to turn yourself in soon.

149
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:51,399
Why should I turn myself in?

150
00:10:52,399 --> 00:10:54,480
The police can't find any evidence of my crimes.

151
00:10:55,879 --> 00:10:56,840
I am a witness.

152
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:58,720
I've already notified Captain Li.

153
00:10:59,519 --> 00:11:01,000
Captain Li is already on his way.

154
00:11:01,679 --> 00:11:02,480
What a shame.

155
00:11:03,279 --> 00:11:05,120
Too bad dead men tell no tales.

156
00:11:08,039 --> 00:11:09,440
But he discovered my secret,

157
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:12,120
so I had to eliminate him to protect myself.

158
00:11:19,039 --> 00:11:19,759
Xing Mingliang!

159
00:11:20,879 --> 00:11:21,720
What are you doing?

160
00:11:22,519 --> 00:11:23,440
What are you doing?

161
00:11:31,879 --> 00:11:32,559
Xing Mingliang!

162
00:11:33,279 --> 00:11:34,000
Xing Mingliang!

163
00:11:45,559 --> 00:11:47,000
Remember this child?

164
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:52,720
I hate children most of all.

165
00:11:56,919 --> 00:11:57,720
Back then,

166
00:11:58,039 --> 00:11:59,799
you were wearing this very pair

167
00:12:00,159 --> 00:12:01,279
of bloodstained gloves

168
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:03,080
when you stroked this child's face,

169
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:07,519
leaving him with a trauma he could never erase.

170
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,679
When this child grew up,

171
00:12:10,039 --> 00:12:11,159
he became a police officer.

172
00:12:12,519 --> 00:12:14,279
He silently swore to himself

173
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,600
that he would catch

174
00:12:16,919 --> 00:12:18,960
this human trafficker in red gloves.

175
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:30,080
So it turns out

176
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,759
karma really does exist.

177
00:12:40,639 --> 00:12:42,639
How many people did you actually kill 22 years ago?

178
00:12:43,159 --> 00:12:44,159
Just one.

179
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,200
She was a whore.

180
00:12:46,559 --> 00:12:47,799
She seduced my father,

181
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,399
and drove my mother to suicide.

182
00:12:49,399 --> 00:12:50,960
So she had to die.

183
00:12:52,679 --> 00:12:53,879
Have you ever considered

184
00:12:54,679 --> 00:12:56,519
that the moment you first raised that knife,

185
00:12:57,039 --> 00:12:58,799
you became the very person you despised?

186
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:02,080
A butcher just like those monsters.

187
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:07,279
You say you wanted revenge.

188
00:13:07,759 --> 00:13:09,240
But what about those innocent children?

189
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:14,960
How many families did you tear apart?

190
00:13:16,639 --> 00:13:18,600
How many parents took their own lives because of you?

191
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,600
What if they came seeking revenge on you?

192
00:13:24,799 --> 00:13:25,759
Killing you a thousand times,

193
00:13:25,759 --> 00:13:26,879
ten thousand times wouldn't be enough.

194
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:30,960
I don't need you to lecture me.

195
00:13:31,639 --> 00:13:32,799
I'm under no obligation to lecture you.

196
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,399
And you don't deserve to be lectured by me.

197
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:37,799
I just want to tell you this:

198
00:13:38,039 --> 00:13:40,799
doing evil in the name of avenging the dead

199
00:13:41,559 --> 00:13:43,519
makes you a thousand times more evil than the real villains,

200
00:13:43,519 --> 00:13:44,320
even ten thousand times more evil.

201
00:13:45,039 --> 00:13:45,919
It's been 22 years.

202
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:48,000
Have you lived like a human being for even a single day?

203
00:13:48,639 --> 00:13:49,559
I did nothing wrong.

204
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,639
They all deserved to die.

205
00:13:52,799 --> 00:13:54,600
They all deserved to die.

206
00:13:54,759 --> 00:13:57,240
They all deserved to die.

207
00:14:00,799 --> 00:14:02,279
I did nothing wrong.

208
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:04,399
I did nothing wrong.

209
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:13,480
It's really all over.

210
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:16,960
Why don't I feel any sense of relief?

211
00:14:18,799 --> 00:14:20,159
Instead, my heart feels heavier and heavier.

212
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:21,639
It's supposed to feel heavy.

213
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:23,600
It means you've matured.

214
00:14:24,240 --> 00:14:26,039
From the evil hidden in these cases,

215
00:14:26,559 --> 00:14:27,960
you've experienced the many sides of human nature.

216
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:30,600
Through these cases,

217
00:14:31,879 --> 00:14:32,799
I've come to understand something.

218
00:14:34,279 --> 00:14:35,120
The net of the law is vast,

219
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:36,440
and nothing slips through.

220
00:14:36,519 --> 00:14:37,200
Those who do evil

221
00:14:37,679 --> 00:14:38,519
will eventually pay the price.

222
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:44,519
From a fatalistic perspective,

223
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:46,200
everyone's fate

224
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:48,519
seems to be pulled by some invisible force.

225
00:14:49,759 --> 00:14:50,759
That's essentially karmic retribution.

226
00:14:51,639 --> 00:14:52,440
Xu Wenwen thought

227
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:54,799
she could run wild on the path of crime.

228
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:56,159
But she overlooked

229
00:14:56,919 --> 00:14:59,080
the unpredictable and inescapable nature of fate.

230
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,720
Every crime she committed

231
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:07,000
would ultimately converge into a righteous judgment.

232
00:15:14,639 --> 00:15:15,279
Captain Li.

233
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:19,440
What a feast.

234
00:15:19,759 --> 00:15:20,519
Who's treating?

235
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,320
I'm in a great mood today.

236
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:24,840
We cracked the big case. Dinner's on me.

237
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:26,200
Great.

238
00:15:27,039 --> 00:15:27,639
Have a seat.

239
00:15:30,159 --> 00:15:30,720
Come on.

240
00:15:33,799 --> 00:15:35,759
Here's to Fengdu staying safe and sound,

241
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:36,759
with no more major cases.

242
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:40,480
May Fengdu never see Red Gloves again.

243
00:15:42,679 --> 00:15:43,200
Cheers.

244
00:15:43,559 --> 00:15:45,320
Come on, cheers.

245
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:45,840
Drink up.

246
00:15:58,440 --> 00:15:59,639
Come on, martial arts master.

247
00:16:00,159 --> 00:16:02,120
Beat me today and you graduate.

248
00:16:02,360 --> 00:16:03,600
We'll officially be partners.

249
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,440
Did you forget how you lost back then?

250
00:16:06,799 --> 00:16:08,840
Forgot I'm a sanda champion?

251
00:16:09,159 --> 00:16:09,840
Hey.

252
00:16:10,519 --> 00:16:12,000
Today I won't get distracted.

253
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:13,679
Bring it on.

254
00:16:14,559 --> 00:16:15,120
Come on.

255
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:21,799
I yield! I yield!

256
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:22,799
I yield!

257
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:23,600
I yield!

258
00:16:23,679 --> 00:16:24,440
What are you doing?

259
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,440
Are you addicted to being an apprentice?

260
00:16:31,639 --> 00:16:32,639
I thought it over.

261
00:16:33,759 --> 00:16:36,120
I think I'll renew my apprentice status.

262
00:16:36,799 --> 00:16:37,639
Being your apprentice,

263
00:16:37,639 --> 00:16:38,679
I get to learn things,

264
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,000
and you look out for me too.

265
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:41,600
I'm getting the bargain of a lifetime.

266
00:17:18,720 --> 00:17:19,400
Dr. Meng,

267
00:17:20,759 --> 00:17:21,599
don't worry.

268
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:24,799
I'll always take care of you

269
00:17:26,119 --> 00:17:27,359
until you get better.

270
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:31,960
So you have to stay strong too.

271
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:41,319
Be upright in character.

272
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:45,200
Be firm in action.

273
00:17:47,599 --> 00:17:48,680
Be sharp in investigation.

274
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:50,400
And in your heart,

275
00:17:50,839 --> 00:17:52,039
always keep the people in mind.

276
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,240
Got it?

277
00:17:58,079 --> 00:17:58,799
Got it,

278
00:17:59,279 --> 00:17:59,920
Master.

279
00:18:00,519 --> 00:18:01,359
Repeat it.

280
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:04,880
Be upright in character.

281
00:18:06,559 --> 00:18:07,640
Be firm in action.

282
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:09,160
Be sharp in investigation.

283
00:18:10,839 --> 00:18:11,559
And in your heart,

284
00:18:12,039 --> 00:18:13,240
always keep the people in mind.
